'''''Peter Pan''''' is a 1984 video game published by [[Hodder & Stoughton]].

==Gameplay==
''Peter Pan'' is a game in which the player is [[Peter Pan]] who encounters characters such as [[Captain Hook]], [[Wendy Darling|Wendy]], [[Tinker Bell|Tinkerbell]], the crocodile, the Indians and Pirates.<ref name="Imagine23"/>

==Reception==
Bill Hoare reviewed ''Peter Pan'' for ''[[Imagine (AD&D magazine)|Imagine]]'' magazine, and stated: "All in all, Peter Pan is an excellent Adventure which should appeal especially to the younger enthusiast and as such it is to be highly recommended."<ref name="Imagine23">{{cite journal | last = Hoare |first = Bill | title =Micro Reviews | type = review | journal = [[Imagine (game magazine)|Imagine]] | issue = 23| pages =45 | publisher = TSR Hobbies (UK), Ltd. |date=February 1985}}</ref>

